== Welcome to the hhlc.eish! ==

This program is tailored to the needs of the HHLC (HAAGA-HELIA Linux Club).
However, if found useful for any other situation, feel free to use, modify and 
redistribute. If so, please make sure that the HHLC logo and name are removed.


== Project Status ==

The project is still under heavy development and is lacking most of its features.
Not recommended for any use besides development.


== Required Gems ==

RedCloth


